    relationship: "Psychology is a science; research methods and evidence evaluation are foundational"

  - id: COMM-101
    relationship: "Communication skills and empathy are central to psychology"

  - id: READ-101
    relationship: "Reading comprehension helps interpret characters' psychological motivations"

  - id: CRIT-101
    relationship: "Critical thinking helps evaluate psychological claims and recognize biases"

  - id: LEARN-101
    relationship: "Learning theory and study strategies are direct applications of psychology"

